==What we want to achieve? ==
We want to create an "alliance" and umbrella project that contains the elements (4 cooperation levels) produced by these group of organisations and projects. This alliance would have its own identity and website, kind of "ring of communities".

We want to connect and give visibility to the emerging phenomena of Commons and Education.

== Cooperation levels ==
Together, we propose to work together in:

# Build a directory of people working in the commons
# exchange curricula and learning materials experience - build a common base of knowledge about the commons
# Incubate/promote concrete projects, initatives and ad hoc networks related with education and commons
# Chart of principles that reflects a common understanding about our goals and vision.

